            <title><![CDATA[Kojima Productions 10th anniversary event ‘Beyond The Strand’ set for September 23]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/09/kojima-productions-10th-anniversary-event-beyond-the-strand-set-for-september-23</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/kojima-productions-10th-anniversary-event-%E2%80%98beyond-the-strand%E2%80%99-set-for-september-23.1285665/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div role="main">
  
  <article>

    
<header>

  <div>

    <ul>
        </ul>

    
    <p><span>Special guest appearances and "a glimpse into future projects."</span>
      </p></div>

  

</header>  

<!-- Moved from templates/posts/default.php -->

    <div><p><a title="Companies > Kojima Productions [561 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/kojima-productions">Kojima Productions</a> will host “Beyond The Strand,” a celebration of 10 years of Kojima Productions, on <a href="https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?iso=20250923T0400" target="_blank">September 23 at 13:00 JST</a> at TOHO Cinemas Roppongi Hills SCREEN7, the company <a href="https://www.kojimaproductions.jp/en/kjp10th_beyond_the_strand" target="_blank">announced</a>. Ticket sales will open via <a href="https://l-tike.com/beyond_the_strand/" target="_blank">Lawson Ticket</a> on <a href="https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?iso=20250902T0100" target="_blank">September 2 at 10:00 JST</a> for 7,700 yen. A live stream is also planned. <span id="more-989466"></span></p><p>The event, hosted by <a title="People > Hideo Kojima [145 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/people/hideo-kojima">Hideo Kojima</a>, will include special guest appearances as well as “a glimpse into future projects.”</p><p>Stay tuned.</p></div>

        
    
