            <title><![CDATA[007 First Light State of Play set for September 3]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/09/007-first-light-state-of-play-set-for-september-3</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/007-first-light-state-of-play-set-for-september-3.1285617/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Featuring over 30 minutes of gameplay.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > Sony Interactive Entertainment [5,048 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sony-group-corporation/sony-interactive-entertainment">Sony Interactive Entertainment</a> and <a title="Companies > IO Interactive [163 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/io-interactive">IO Interactive</a> will host a <em><a title="Games > 007 First Light [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/007-first-light">007 First Light</a></em>-focused <a title="Platforms > PlayStation [48,415 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation">PlayStation</a> State of Play broadcast on <a href="https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?iso=20250903T1800" target="_blank">September 3 at 11:00 a.m. PT / 2:00 p.m. ET</a>, the companies <a href="https://blog.playstation.com/2025/09/01/state-of-play-presents-007-first-light-gameplay-deep-dive-on-september-3/" target="_blank">announced</a>. You will be able to watch it on <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pwRpK8eoLLE" target="_blank">YouTube</a> (<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o3S4qXOarxM" target="_blank">Subtitled</a>) and <a href="https://twitch.tv/PlayStation" target="_blank">Twitch</a>. <span id="more-989446"></span></p><p>The broadcast will feature over 30 minutes of gameplay, including a playthrough of James Bond’s first mission as an MI6 recruit, followed by insights from IO Interactive.</p><p><em>007 First Light</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,290 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [7,837 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [381 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [24,141 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3768760/007_First_Light/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a> and <a href="https://store.epicgames.com/p/007-first-light-182cea" target="_blank">Epic Games Store</a> in 2026.</p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/09/007-first-light-state-of-play-set-for-september-3]]></content:encoded>
